I guess the first thing to say is they're
a consequence of general relativity that

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:06.920
when you get as far as writing down the
equations of general relativity and start

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:10.690
trying to solve them you find that some
of the solutions involve these wave solutions.

00:00:10.690 --> 00:00:15.369
They're distortions of the spacetime that propagate out.
-I mean they're important

00:00:15.380 --> 00:00:18.780
for lots of reasons they're important
because they are a prediction of general

00:00:18.789 --> 00:00:21.841
relativity so actually if you then
detect them you've found further

00:00:21.841 --> 00:00:24.999
confirmation that general relativity is actually right.
-Whenever matter

00:00:25.019 --> 00:00:29.109
passes by through some region of spacetime it will distort the spacetime just like

00:00:29.109 --> 00:00:33.730
you would distort water when if you
put your fingers through water and waves

00:00:33.739 --> 00:00:38.649
propagate out this is a propagation of the
spacetime itself, so the spacetime is

00:00:38.649 --> 00:00:41.390
is sort of moving in and out,

00:00:41.390 --> 00:00:45.720
propagating out at the speed of light.
