00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:28.360
but they were both 30 to 40
solar mass black holes. So those are the

00:05:28.370 --> 00:05:31.710
kind of black holes which are probably
the end states of very massive stars,

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:35.370
although they are actually on the high
